Package: svytest
Type: Package
Title: Survey Weight Diagnostic Tests
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Corbin", "Lubianski",
      email = "cnlubianski@yahoo.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0009-0547-3249")
    )
  )
Description: Provides diagnostic tests for assessing informativeness of survey 
    weights in regression models. Implements weighted-adjusted tests, 
    difference-in-coefficients, estimating-equation approaches, and 
    permutation-based methods. Helps analysts decide whether to incorporate 
    survey weights in analytic inference, particularly linear regressions.
